///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// File: socket.mh
//
// Desc: MEX socket intrinsics for outgoing TCP connections and HTTP
//       convenience. Connect to remote services, send/receive raw data,
//       or make one-shot HTTP requests — all with timeout control.
